726847f-b.text:
Hillside Avenue, at Braddock Avenue, looking eastward across the Cottage Gardens Company tree nurseries, and showing the terminus of Hillside Avenue. The truck is turning down Braddock Avenue. Some years later Hillside Avenue was extended and cut through the
land occupied by the nurseries.
View 2 was taken from Hillside Avenue, just weat of Braddock Avenue, looking south and shows new real estate development.
P. L. Sperr  March 4, 1927
